properties.description: The following arguments are supported:

properties.name: project_id
properties.description: • project_id - (Required) An associated Selectel VPC project. Changing this creates a new floating IP.

properties.name: region
properties.description: • region - (Required) A region of where the floating IP resides. Changing this creates a new floating IP.
The following arguments are supported:

properties.name: name
properties.description: • name - (Required) Name of the keypair. Changing this creates a new keypair.

properties.name: public_key
properties.description: • public_key - (Required) A pregenerated OpenSSH-formatted public key. Changing this creates a new keypair.

properties.name: regions
properties.description: • regions - (Optional) List of region names where keypair is need to be created. Keypair will be created in all available regions if omitted. Changing this creates a new keypair.

properties.name: user_id
properties.description: • user_id - (Required) An associated Selectel VPC user. Changing this creates a new keypair.
The following arguments are supported:

properties.name: project_id
properties.description: • project_id - (Required) An associated Selectel VPC project. Changing this creates a new license.

properties.name: region
properties.description: • region - (Required) A region of where the license resides. Changing this creates a new license.

properties.name: type
properties.description: • type - (Required) The type of license. Changing this creates a new license.
The following arguments are supported:

properties.name: name
properties.description: • name - (Required) The name of the project.

properties.name: custom_url
properties.description: • custom_url - (Optional) The custom url for the project. Needs to be the 3rd-level domain for the selvpc.ru. Example: terraform-project-001.selvpc.ru.

properties.name: theme
properties.description: • theme - (Optional) An additional theme settings for this project. The structure is described below.

properties.name: auto_quotas
properties.description: • auto_quotas - (Optional) A boolean parameter that specifies if project should get automatically calculated quotas.

properties.name: quotas
properties.description: • quotas - (Optional) An array of desired quotas for this project. The structure is described below.
The theme block supports:

properties.name: color
properties.description: • color - (Optional) A background color in hex format.

properties.name: logo
properties.description: • logo - (Optional) An url of the project header logo.
The quotas block supports:

properties.name: resource_name
properties.description: • resource_name - (Required) A name of the billing resource to set quotas for.

properties.name: resource_quotas
properties.description: • resource_quotas - (Required) An array of desired billing quotas for this particular resource. The structure is described below.
The resource_quotas block supports:

properties.name: region
properties.description: • region - (Optional) A Selectel VPC region for the resource quota.

properties.name: zone
properties.description: • zone - (Optional) A Selectel VPC zone for the resource quota.

properties.name: value
properties.description: • value - (Required) A value of the resource quota.
The following arguments are supported:

properties.name: project_id
properties.description: • project_id - (Required) An associated Selectel VPC project. Changing this creates a new role.

properties.name: user_id
properties.description: • user_id - (Required) An associated Selectel VPC user. Changing this creates a new role.
The following arguments are supported:

properties.name: project_id
properties.description: • project_id - (Required) An associated Selectel VPC project. Changing this creates a new subnet.

properties.name: region
properties.description: • region - (Required) A region of where the subnet resides. Changing this creates a new subnet.

properties.name: prefix_length
properties.description: • prefix_length - (Optional) A prefix length of the subnet. Defaults to 29. Changing this creates a new subnet.

properties.name: ip_version
properties.description: • ip_version - (Optional) A version of the IP protocol of the subnet. Defaults to "ipv4". Changing this creates a new subnet.
The following arguments are supported:

properties.name: project_id
properties.description: • project_id - (Optional) An associated Selectel VPC project. Changing this creates a new token.

properties.name: account_name
properties.description: • account_name - (Optional) An associated Selectel VPC account. Changing this creates a new token.
The following arguments are supported:

properties.name: name
properties.description: • name - (Required) Name of the user. Changing this updates the name of the existing user.

properties.name: password
properties.description: • password - (Required) Password of the user. Changing this updates the password of the existing user.

properties.name: enabled
properties.description: • enabled - (Optional) Enabled state of the user. Changing this updates the enabled state of the existing user.
The following arguments are supported:

properties.name: project_id
properties.description: • project_id - (Required) An associated Selectel VPC project. Changing this creates a new VRRP subnet.

properties.name: master_region
properties.description: • master_region - (Required) A master region of where the VRRP subnet resides. Changing this creates a new VRRP subnet.

properties.name: slave_region
properties.description: • slave_region - (Required) A slave region of where the VRRP subnet resides. Changing this creates a new VRRP subnet.

properties.name: prefix_length
properties.description: • prefix_length - (Optional) A prefix length of the VRRP subnet. Defaults to 29. Changing this creates a new VRRP subnet.

properties.name: ip_version
properties.description: • ip_version - (Optional) A version of the IP protocol of the VRRP subnet. Defaults to "ipv4". Changing this creates a new VRRP subnet.
